Preconditions:
The input matrix `mat` must not be null.
The input matrix `mat` must be a square matrix, i.e., the number of rows must be equal to the number of columns.

Postconditions:
The method should return an integer value representing the sum of the matrix diagonals.
The sum of the matrix diagonals should be calculated correctly.
If the input matrix `mat` is empty (0x0 matrix), the method should return 0 as the sum of diagonals.